Cell["\<\
Exercise1
After entering the following definitions for f, use Timing and ListLogPlot to \
make a plot with a logarithmic vertical scale of the time needed to evaluate \
f[n] for n from 1 to 30:\
\>", "Subsection",
 CellChangeTimes->{{3.9857908223877735`*^9, 
  3.9857908344635296`*^9}},ExpressionUUID->"e6fe31cf-4f4d-4641-b994-\
